parameters:
Welcomeee!! Currently, here are the available subquests you
can take on!!

I just got transferred, so I'm all over the place...! Do
this... and that...!

Magic is definitely the strongest, isn't it? The stability
that it provides is different from what physical abilities
can offer.

What is the 'strongest' is such a futile debate... The
strongest technique is to strike with the strongest
'timing.' That is the true 'strongest.' Don't you think so
too?

Physical is definitely the strongest, right? The explosive
power that magic lacks is different.

We're thinking of moving to Yurisine and getting married.
Plus, we can pass on the guild's work.

Even after the war ends, the guild's work never decreases,
huh? It's just that people's troubles change into something
else.
\i[513] Obtained the truth of the world! \$
